reviewText: To start off with this was ordered for a friend. When I order movies for friends I check them before turning them over to new owner. The DVD is just as it was described,  And she is tickled to death.
Have given these to the horse lovers in my life and they watch them over and over.  It was worth getting.

I grew up on Flicka from the stories my father would tell me.  Would recommend these stores because they are clean and somewhat informative.
These are great for the younger child in all of us.
